FBIS3-55044 "drsov003_b_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Stepankov Fired LD0401180394 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1700 GMT 4 Jan 94 LD0401180394 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Excerpt] [passage omitted] During a news conference in Omsk today, Russian Federation Procurator General Aleksey Kazannik also said he has signed a decree on sacking his predecessor, Valentin Stepankov, from the procuracy bodies. His participation in corruption is currently under investigation by the Moscow Procuracy. At the same time, similar material regarding former Security Minister Viktor Barannikov and Deputy Interior Minister Andrey Dunayev has already been checked, and criminal charges of corruption are to be laid against them soon.
